{"tid":463544,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】強烈要求所以同伴都係女角!! Day146 9/11 【DQXI】","createTime":"2017-11-09T14:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T17:53:48.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3790b21227c09fbe7521fb28d2ef61c7ddf40946","tid":463544,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T14:53:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=NI4zM6uo3QlXP9oK1b6soZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ee32e6aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，開台前或者有任何突發事唔開都會Po上FB。<br />\n有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=NI4zM6uo3QlXP9oK1b6soZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=55a98c5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NRSeWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNRSeWz.jpg&h=f4a261d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我亦開左個Youtuber Page放開台嘅Backup<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg&d=NI4zM6uo3QlXP9oK1b6soZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=e82e2911\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com